{"tid":1822580,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"集中行動 重整連登風氣!","createTime":"2020-01-13T05:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T12:32:35.000Z","uid":222374,"like":82,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"362344dcde3043e028942314e044aad7d378c176","tid":1822580,"uid":222374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:01:06.000Z","msg":"留意左好耐， 每逢一到晚上時間<br />\n就會不停有一啲批鬥，分化，風向post沖曬上去熱門<br />\n本來嗰啲行動post就全部沉曬底<br />\n第二日就自然冇人睇<br />\n你哋出其他post，回覆嘅人麻煩就不推文<br />\n唔好洗走熱門的行動post好唔好， 你哋咪自己不推文討論囉!<br />\n<br />\n咁得閒上連登講乜嘢影人大頭， 又要批鬥<br />\n貼連儂牆文宣嗰陣就唔見你哋一齊幫手?<br />\n和你影不如和你貼喇! 搞好個社會風氣先好冇<br />\n而家班撕紙狗撕得咁勁， 專心返和你貼先啦<br />\n<br />\n講起和你貼，已經有人出post講明點樣可以加大效率!<br />\n[行動]連儂/文宣都可以十八區開花! A4 label周圍貼! 大量現成圖-即print 即貼(2)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1819022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1819022</a><br />\n<br />\n認同就like下， 唔鍾意嘅就dislike<br />\n話我知有乜嘢做錯<br />\n<br />\n我預左咗又畀人屌㗎喇， 但係麻煩真係專注返場運動， 我哋七個月以嚟手足嘅付出唔係 condom!<br />\n<br />\n上個post推極都推唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccae3c61b0108d4c6924ee450cf4ea21b422868","tid":1822580,"uid":222374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:02:04.000Z","msg":"呢次唔會又推唔喐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LTwa199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLTwa199.jpg&h=a96879b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5XahJv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5XahJv.jpg&h=75963323&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f952678fc9b9a398d777e7589ae5a5b47661cc3","tid":1822580,"uid":222374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tffOOQu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtffOOQu.jpg&h=649c3f2